# =============================================================
# OKX (Ouyi) Ruleset for Loon (Comprehensive)
#
# Description: An exhaustive ruleset for all OKX/OKEx/Ouyi
# services, including web, app, APIs, WebSockets, and
# third-party dependencies (KYC, Captcha, Analytics).
#
# Author: Gemini
# Last Updated: 2025-11-16
# =============================================================

# Part 1: Core Domains (OKX)
# 核心域名 (OKX 品牌)
# Covers main website, app APIs, and WebSocket endpoints.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okx.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okx.media
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okx-sec.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okx-static.com

# Part 2: Legacy Domains (OKEx)
# 历史域名 (OKEx 品牌)
# Still used for redirects, assets, or old API versions.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okex.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okex.media

# Part 3: Regional & Alternative Domains (Ouyi)
# 区域与备用域名 (欧易品牌)
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, ouyi.exchange
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, ouyi.com

# Part 4: Parent Company & Core CDN
# 母公司及核心 CDN
# OK Group and associated static asset domains.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okg.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okg-static.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okx.cdn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, okx-cdn.com

# Part 5: Critical Third-Party Services
# 关键第三方服务
# Required for app functionality (Captcha, KYC, Analytics).
# -------------------------------------------------------------
# Captcha (验证码)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, hcaptcha.com
DOMAIN, www.google.com
DOMAIN, www.recaptcha.net

# KYC (身份认证)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, jumio.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, sumsub.com

# Analytics & Error Tracking (应用分析与错误追踪)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, datadoghq.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, sentry.io

# Support (客服系统)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, zendesk.com

# Part 6: Keyword Fallbacks
# 关键词回落 (兜底规则)
# Catches any other related subdomains or new domains.
# -------------------------------------------------------------
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, okx
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, okex
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, ouyi
DOMAIN-KEYWORD, okgroup
